{"id": 1537, "genre": 1001, "title": "你最讨厌做的家务是什么？", "description": "虽然我知道每一项家务活你都不喜欢做，但哪个是你最讨厌的？（题图来自：Maira Kalman ​​​​）", "record_count": 4475, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170224014439laOuUBowih0crAkW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-01T03:00:18Z", "options": [{"id": 172800, "content": "每次看到床上那一摊，内心是炸裂的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952609}, {"id": 173056, "content": "一切家务都讨厌，有限的生命不想被无限的家务浪费掉...", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810976}, {"id": 174848, "content": "做饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958198}, {"id": 172545, "content": "什么是家务ㄟ( ▔, ▔ )ㄏ", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952753}, {"id": 172801, "content": "洗碗 和清理很脏的水渍", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902818}, {"id": 173057, "content": "我真的不理解为啥要叠被", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907050}, {"id": 173825, "content": "洗碗。爱做饭，不爱收拾和洗碗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949252}, {"id": 174081, "content": "最讨厌洗衣服", "image": "img/option/option/20170303164731Q42kAgwozhKerdxp.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956242}, {"id": 175361, "content": "洗油腻腻的碗筷，都是食物残渣的餐具", "image": "img/option/option/20170306210537VZule1cQf0x94NAy", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960638}, {"id": 176385, "content": "洗衣服没有之一！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962735}, {"id": 172546, "content": "最不喜欢洗碗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 200394}, {"id": 172802, "content": "在校的时候  洗衣服简直是要人命", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953256}, {"id": 172803, "content": "我是擦地板会逼死自己的严重强迫症患者，对地上的头发蜜汁神经紧张。只要不让我擦地板，什么都好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707545}, {"id": 173059, "content": "洗碗和做饭一天只能做一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808967}, {"id": 174339, "content": "换被套", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732825}, {"id": 172548, "content": "做饭，洗碗可以真心不想做饭太累了", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952756}, {"id": 172804, "content": "洗碗", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953258}, {"id": 173828, "content": "独自换被套", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652118}, {"id": 174852, "content": "做家务没意见啊?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957845}, {"id": 172549, "content": "都不喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761842}, {"id": 172805, "content": "喜欢做家务", "image": "img/option/option/20170301170103PKgCWDu9iovbB3JT", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950395}, {"id": 173061, "content": "洗碗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529538}, {"id": 172550, "content": "除草", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155388}, {"id": 172806, "content": "刷碗！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953262}, {"id": 172551, "content": "洗碗 没有之一", "image": null, "praise_count": 438, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609428}, {"id": 172807, "content": "做饭不洗碗，洗衣服不晾，扫地不擦地", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953271}, {"id": 175367, "content": "洗碗，到没有什么可讨厌，因为我天天干。而父母玩手机电脑，我每天写作业还要刷碗?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960659}, {"id": 172552, "content": "晾衣服（竟然不是洗衣服）！！\r\n讨厌黏糊糊的手感，爱死了发明烘干机的人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686283}, {"id": 172808, "content": "换床单和被套\r\n自从有了洗碗机，烘干机，扫地拖地机器人，啥时候有换床单被套机器人啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913616}, {"id": 173064, "content": "下水道疏通……各种头发和油污", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949713}, {"id": 174344, "content": "洗碗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 789146}, {"id": 177416, "content": "洗菜特别是肉菜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335818}, {"id": 182280, "content": "套被罩", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978832}, {"id": 172553, "content": "对于做饭难吃的人，当然是做饭了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 195865}, {"id": 173065, "content": "我真的不理解人为什么要每天洗澡，吃了饭为什么还要洗碗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953927}, {"id": 177417, "content": "收拾屋子?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948386}, {"id": 208906, "content": "杀鱼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809902}, {"id": 172810, "content": "洗碗 因为超冷", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951773}, {"id": 175626, "content": "洗衣服呀！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 961319}, {"id": 172555, "content": "做饭。。。。不喜欢所以就不想学。油烟太大，怕油会溅出来。而且不喜欢摸到油油的油壶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952771}, {"id": 172811, "content": "洗澡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 863475}, {"id": 173067, "content": "擦窗，还好有专门的保洁公司", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050842}, {"id": 174603, "content": "不喜欢拖地，别的啥都行。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957834}, {"id": 172556, "content": "做家务", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747674}, {"id": 172812, "content": "洗碗！洗碗不只是要洗碗！还有灶台！锅！擦桌子！倒垃圾！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 150304}, {"id": 173068, "content": "拖地", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948662}, {"id": 173580, "content": "家务本身", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 662304}, {"id": 172557, "content": "拖地，拖地", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952778}, {"id": 172813, "content": "收拾", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886108}, {"id": 173069, "content": "我只喜欢帮家人做家务 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953938}]}